   "Model" -> <|"Service" -> "OpenAI", "Name" -> "gpt-5.4"|>, "Temperature" -> 
   1, "OriginalCellString" -> 
   "Cell[\"For complex features spanning multiple sessions, a manual approach \
to context management often works better. Here we'll describe an example \
workflow that efficiently manages context. The core idea: instead of \
continuing one long conversation, start fresh sessions with carefully curated \
context.\", \"Text\", CellID -> 545559776]"|>,
